code: @Test public void testGenerateUUID() {     JavaUuidGenerator uuidGenerator = new JavaUuidGenerator().     String firstUUID = uuidGenerator.generateUuid().     String secondUUID = uuidGenerator.generateUuid().     assertTrue(firstUUID.matches("^\\w{8}-\\w{4}-\\w{4}-\\w{4}-\\w{12}$")).     assertTrue(secondUUID.matches("^\\w{8}-\\w{4}-\\w{4}-\\w{4}-\\w{12}$")).     assertFalse(firstUUID.equals(secondUUID)). }

@Test public void testPerformance() {     JavaUuidGenerator uuidGenerator = new JavaUuidGenerator().     StopWatch watch = new StopWatch().     LOG.info("First id: " + uuidGenerator.generateUuid()).     for (int i = 0. i < 500000. i++) {         uuidGenerator.generateUuid().     }     LOG.info("Last id:  " + uuidGenerator.generateUuid()).
